	<span>6. Using This Website Contrary To Applicable Laws And Regulations, Or In A Way That Causes, Or May Cause, Harm To The Website, Or To Any Person Or Business Entity;</span><br>
	<span>7. Engaging In Any Data Mining, Data Harvesting, Data Extracting Or Any Other Similar Activity In Relation To This Website, Or While Using This Website;</span><br>
	<span>8. Using This Website To Engage In Any Advertising Or Marketing;</span>
			</p>
			
		</div>
